OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778217995
OL,3,CLorry carrying a digger hits two
OL,4,Cbridges in East Yorkshire
OL,6,FThere has been major travel disruption
OL,7,Fin East Yorkshire after a lorry
OL,8,Fcarrying a digger hit two bridges over
OL,9,Fthe A63.
OL,11,FThe vehicle caused damage to both the
OL,12,FWelton Road bridge and the Dale Road
OL,13,Fbridge, with the incident occurring
OL,14,Fshortly after 3pm on Wednesday 6 May.
OL,16,FFollowing the damage, the westbound
OL,17,Fcarriageway of the A63 is closed
OL,18,Fbetween the A15 Humber Bridge and the
OL,19,FA1034 at South Cave.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
