FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778217995
OL,3,CLorry carrying a digger hits two
OL,4,Cbridges in East Yorkshire
OL,6,FThe Dale Road bridge has been struck
OL,7,Fpreviously, including more than two
OL,8,Fyears ago by a lorry carrying a
OL,9,Fforklift truck. The bridge has
OL,10,Fremained partially closed since.
OL,12,FNational Highways says repair works
OL,13,Fare being arranged but there is no
OL,14,Festimated time for completion.
OL,16,FIt also added that a "structures
OL,17,Finspector is currently on site
OL,18,Fassessing both bridges to understand
OL,19,Fthe extent and severity of the damage.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,366,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1778217995
OL,3,CLorry carrying a digger hits two
OL,4,Cbridges in East Yorkshire
OL,6,F"Detailed structural inspections must
OL,7,Fbe completed to determine whether the
OL,8,Fbridges are safe for traffic or if
OL,9,Ffurther measures, such as repairs are
OL,10,Frequired before reopening.
OL,12,F"These assessments are essential to
OL,13,Fensure the safety of road users and
OL,14,Fcannot be rushed. Until we have
OL,15,Fconfirmation that it is safe to do so,
OL,16,Fthe A63 westbound will remain closed."
OL,18,FHumberside Police is asking motorists
OL,19,Fto avoid the area, with officers in
OL,20,Fattendance.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
